  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study looked at short-wire ERCP devices versus Long-wire ERCP devices. The study
      hypothesis is to compare the performance of the Fusion ERCP short-wire system to the
      traditional Long-wire system.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
